  "1043260": {
    "name": "角斗士公会经理",
    "steam_appid": 1043260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣首批角斗士，在这个史诗般的奇幻世界中开启您的冒险之旅吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/965d379147e1ca1351f95125740d0965.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/965d379147e1ca1351f95125740d0965.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/965d379147e1ca1351f95125740d0965.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角逐竞技场争霸赛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为每场战斗精心挑选角斗士，排兵布阵，并发号施令。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/e4796ca9ff709b871de76a810453edfb.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/e4796ca9ff709b871de76a810453edfb.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/e4796ca9ff709b871de76a810453edfb.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗将自动进行，最终展示您的战术成果。密切关注敌人的动向，了解他们的一举一动，以找出最佳的反制手段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的目标是赢得所有竞技场争霸赛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/ce74f00cd40fd45cc1591c6a3346dfb0.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/ce74f00cd40fd45cc1591c6a3346dfb0.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/ce74f00cd40fd45cc1591c6a3346dfb0.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩充您的队伍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏的深入，您可以建造新的建筑，这样就能雇佣新的角斗士类型，包括战士、弓箭手、野兽、法师等，打造独一无二的战队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/03cf4acb4a426ac709c21409bd00000f.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/03cf4acb4a426ac709c21409bd00000f.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/03cf4acb4a426ac709c21409bd00000f.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角斗士的特质决定了其能够获得的加成和额外技能。您可以在市场上发掘超值交易，或者在制定战术时培养和升级角斗士的特质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/87659ee0088a5770b02b8a264f9f9c19.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/87659ee0088a5770b02b8a264f9f9c19.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/87659ee0088a5770b02b8a264f9f9c19.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在培养独一无二的战队的过程中，您将尽情释放自己的创造力。您需要提升角斗士的等级，升级他们的特质，并装备强大的物品，同时精心谋划如何打造一支高效协同的角斗士战队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每月锦标赛的间隙，您应该抓紧一切机会获取利润和成长，以便在下一轮锦标赛中占据优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加每周的死亡擂台竞技场活动，接受各种提供不同的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操纵能够影响角斗士的天象，从而在和对手的对战中占据上风。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/dcdd062f16db7ed72f48a2547e6ee6a0.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/dcdd062f16db7ed72f48a2547e6ee6a0.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/dcdd062f16db7ed72f48a2547e6ee6a0.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务与世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在竞技场之外，各个派别会邀请您参加各种任务，需要您的角斗士发起致命打击，这将建立或摧毁在这些派别中的声望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以选择资助贫民，支持地区和王国，或是推动魔法界的发展，具体取决于您选择的主要效忠阵营。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/260fc25553a5789a051f875964bd0e69.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/260fc25553a5789a051f875964bd0e69.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/260fc25553a5789a051f875964bd0e69.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改变该地区和王国的命运，或者参与有趣的支线剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您准备好接受终极考验时，接受具有挑战性的任务，您的战队将与恐怖的怪物首领进行战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/b22390a70166304a3da0d3f62941010a.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/b22390a70166304a3da0d3f62941010a.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/b22390a70166304a3da0d3f62941010a.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>耐玩性</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏时，您可以选择不同的主要效忠阵营，这将导致不同的主线任务和结局，您还可可以尝试不同的战队策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锦标赛模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成主线剧情后，您可以尝试无尽锦标赛模式，游戏模式会简化为回合制。您遇到的敌人会越来越强大，直至战斗失败为止。Steam排行榜将记录您的得分，列出您与其他玩家或好友排名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/6f2d0bf6a76ecda8cf15f246b728551c.poster.avif?t=1770992196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/6f2d0bf6a76ecda8cf15f246b728551c.webm?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043260/extras/6f2d0bf6a76ecda8cf15f246b728551c.mp4?t=1770992196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>社区</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常欢迎您加入我们的  社区，听取您对游戏的反馈和体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
